#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_networkedmultiplayerpeer.rst:137
msgid ""
"**TARGET_PEER_BROADCAST** = **0** --- Packets are sent to the server and "
"then redistributed to other peers."
msgstr ""

